            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">Correspondence and leaflets relating to the administration and finances of Stanford University and to American participation in World War I. Correspondence mostly with Herbert Hoover. Includes a series of leaflets by E. D. Adams, entitled 
                <title render="italic">Why We Are at War</title> with Germany, 1918. Includes photocopied correspondence.</abstract>
